songs.title: Jesus Loves Me More Than He Loves You
songs.lyrics:
[Unknown:]
Jesus loves me more than he

[Chorus - Brendon and Unknown:]
Loves you
And Jesus is in love with everything I do
When I touch myself every day
Jesus' love comes shining through
'Cause Jesus loves me more than he loves you

[Brendon:]
A man, with muscles of steel
And his love is just as real
